{"featured_counts":5,"common_counts":187,"collapsed_counts":1,"reviewing_counts":0,"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/560685409/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=49\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/560685409/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=47\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","totals":82},"data":[{"id":566754176,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/566754176","content":"设对数学研究的人的集合有：存粹热爱数学的人和各种投机学数学的人。\u003cbr\u003e前提：只要对数学真理的评判标准不变，投机人研究出来的数学和热爱数学的人研究出来的数学没有任何区别。\u003cbr\u003e推论：那么数学研究领域大的集合概率上对数学领域的推动必定比小的集合大。\u003cbr\u003e结论：题主想要保证学数学的纯粹性，来证明学数学是多么多么热爱数学，其他凡是有一点不纯粹的人不配学数学，同时直接说投机的人学数学好的就是为了灌水，坏的就是学术不端，而忽略了学术领域对数学研究成果的评判是一视同仁的。最后不管学数学是什么目的，不管你怎么主观的说这样对别人不好，只要评判标准不变，哪怕投机的人良莠不齐，概率上也会提高对这个领域的推动的可能性。","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1545967135,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"e9d3aad1a75e34a516f12f83905054e3","url_token":"17381593445","name":"喵酱","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-9ca12093d70661cfbd41353320b8ef41_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-9ca12093d70661cfbd41353320b8ef41_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/e9d3aad1a75e34a516f12f83905054e3","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":0,"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0,"child_comment_count":3,"child_comments":[{"id":566779004,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/566779004","content":"不是的，你曲解了我的很多意思。你的前提和推论和结论我也都不认同。我也没有说不纯粹的人不配学数学。\u003cbr\u003e我之所以发声就是因为我不认同你的最后的论断。一个领域不自己努力净化推进自己领域，单单希望靠固定的标准来推动自己领域，这是不可能的。我作为从业人员，更知道一个领域多么容易变得浮躁最后堕落。","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1545970006,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"author","member":{"id":"a372f9163fc796528e3b5078fa079613","url_token":"sun-ao-74","name":"Sun Ao","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2e8103860f015822f4ca9893bab2a726_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2e8103860f015822f4ca9893bab2a726_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/a372f9163fc796528e3b5078fa079613","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[{"type":"best_answerer","description":"优秀回答者"}],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":2,"reply_to_author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"e9d3aad1a75e34a516f12f83905054e3","url_token":"17381593445","name":"喵酱","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-9ca12093d70661cfbd41353320b8ef41_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-9ca12093d70661cfbd41353320b8ef41_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/e9d3aad1a75e34a516f12f83905054e3","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false}},"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0},{"id":566899302,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/566899302","content":"固定的标准是唯一的，却是最有效的，如今查重技术已经可以甄别一切录入数据库的抄袭了。\u003cbr\u003e答主的净化标准是什么呢？靠热爱数学的程度？堕落的标准又是什么呢？如果有其他目的的人得到成果就算是堕落？\u003cbr\u003e既然是一个行业就有自己的一个规矩，但是没有哪个行业的规矩是只要热爱就完事了吧。计算机行业也有很多培训班的人涌入，也没有说一群老牌程序员抵制吧。只能说答主把学数学当成信仰了。","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1545985027,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":t